      <title>152 次测试即将来临，日元押注创 17 年来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/bets-against-yen-at-highest-in-17-years-as-test-of-152-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者对日元下跌的押注达到了 17 年来的最高水平，此时日元正徘徊在关键水平附近，这将增加日本干预的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/bets-against-yen-at-highest-in-17-years-as-test-of-152-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 00:46:41 GMT</pubDate>
