    <item>
      <title>力拓任命资深人士巴塔尔为商务主管，推动增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/rio-appoints-veteran-baatar-as-commercial-chief-amid-growth-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[力拓集团 (Rio Tinto Group) 任命资深高管博尔德·巴塔尔 (Bold Baatar) 为首席商务官，这家全球第二大矿业公司寻求铜等关键材料的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/rio-appoints-veteran-baatar-as-commercial-chief-amid-growth-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 00:04:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国国家银行请求法院清算开发商世茂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/chinese-developer-shimao-receives-wind-up-petition-in-hong-kong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的中国开发商世茂集团控股有限公司正面临债权人中国建设银行（亚洲）股份有限公司的清算要求，这是迄今为止国有银行试图从陷入困境的开发商收回资金的最突出例子之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/chinese-developer-shimao-receives-wind-up-petition-in-hong-kong</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:55:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本实际工资下降可能导致日本央行暂时按兵不动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/japan-s-real-wages-fall-for-23rd-month-as-price-growth-picks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者价格上涨加速，日本工人的实际工资在 2 月份连续 23 个月下降，拖累了支出，这一结果可能会让央行暂时按兵不动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/japan-s-real-wages-fall-for-23rd-month-as-price-growth-picks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油集会因以色列撤走部分加沙军队而暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列表示将从加沙撤出部分军队，油价五个交易日以来首次下跌，交易员正在等待本周一系列市场报告，这些报告将提供有关供需的概况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:26:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市跟随美国上涨，人民币汇率稳定：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/asian-stocks-set-for-gains-eyes-on-daily-yuan-fix-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五美国就业数据好于预期后，亚洲股市跟随华尔街上涨。由于以色列表示将从加沙撤出部分军队，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/asian-stocks-set-for-gains-eyes-on-daily-yuan-fix-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国央行连续第 17 个月购买黄金，金价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-pboc-buys-gold-for-17th-month-as-prices-hit-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份，中国央行连续第17个月购买黄金作为储备，延续了购买热潮，帮助贵金属飙升至创纪录水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-pboc-buys-gold-for-17th-month-as-prices-hit-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 08:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
